# Navigation example: move through multiple real Wikipedia pages and verify each stop.
url https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_testing

describe "Wikipedia navigation"
  test "follows links across related topics"
    Verify the page heading says "Software testing"
    Click the "Test automation" link
    Verify the page heading says "Test automation"
    Click the "Continuous testing" link
    Verify the page heading says "Continuous testing"
